## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available online resources and may not encompass all possible actions that social institutions can take. The search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude relevant information from non-English speaking regions. Additionally, the effectiveness of the proposed actions can vary depending on the specific cultural and social context of each institution. Further research and localized studies are recommended to tailor these actions to specific communities.